itualist_CF_SeeInvisibility|True	FACT:Spiritualist_CF_FusedConsciousness|True	FACT:Spiritualist_CF_CallSpirit|True										ASPECT:Archetype Base Class|Spiritualist
Priest of the Fallen	KEY:Spiritualist Archetype ~ Priest of the Fallen	SOURCEPAGE:p.17	CATEGORY:Archetype	TYPE:Archetype.SpiritualistArchetype	PRECLASS:1,Spiritualist=1	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Spiritualist Archetype ~ Priest of the Fallen],[!PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,Spiritualist_Archetype_BondedManifestation=True,Spiritualist_Archetype_EctoplasmicBondedManifestation=True,Spiritualist_Archetype_IncorporealBondedManifestation=True,Spiritualist_Archetype_PhantomRecall=True,Spiritualist_Archetype_DualBond=True]	DESC:Countless hero-gods have risen and fallen through Iblydos’s long  history, leaving behind mighty spirits. Those attuned to these fallen hero-gods can become conduits for their restless souls and agents acting out their divine will. The result is a priest of the fallen, a spiritualist who channels her land’s legends and provides a vessel for mighty heroes to perform heroic acts once more.				ABILITY:Spiritualist Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Priest of the Fallen ~ Mythmaker	ABILITY:Spiritualist Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Priest of the Fallen ~ Channel Energy|PRECLASS:1,Spiritualist=3	ABILITY:Spiritualist Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Priest of the Fallen ~ Phantom Call|PRECLASS:1,Spiritualist=6	ABILITY:Spiritualist Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Priest of the Fallen ~ Masterful Faith|PRECLASS:1,Spiritualist=17	ABILITY:Spiritualist Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Priest of the Fallen ~ True Legend|PRECLASS:1,Spiritualist=20																																															COST:0	FACT:Spiritualist_Archetype_BondedManifestation|True	FACT:Spiritualist_Archetype_EctoplasmicBondedManifestation|True	FACT:Spiritualist_Archetype_IncorporealBondedManifestation|True	FACT:Spiritualist_Archetype_PhantomRecall|True	FACT:Spiritualist_Archetype_DualBond|True	FACT:Spiritualist_CF_BondedManifestation|True	FACT:Spiritualist_CF_EctoplasmicBondedManifestation|True	FACT:Spiritualist_CF_IncorporealBondedManifestation|True	FACT:Spiritualist_CF_PhantomRecall|True	FACT:Spiritualist_CF_DualBond|True	ASPE