Spirit Eater		KEY:Medium Archetype ~ Spirit Eater				SOURCEPAGE:p.24	CATEGORY:Archetype	TYPE:Archetype.MediumArchetype		PRECLASS:1,Medium=1		PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Medium Archetype ~ Spirit Eater],[!PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,Medium_Archetype_HauntChanneler=True,Medium_Archetype_LocationChannel=True,Medium_Archetype_ConnectionChannel=True]																									DESC:Shenmen is a ghost-haunted nation trapped in the shadow of  the Gossamer Mountains and held beneath the yoke of jorogumo witches. The mediums of Shenmen face brazen yokai that hunger for the living, and these mediums have learned to devour them instead. Guardians of their communities, spirit eaters absorb the dead to channel their power and serve as a line of defense against all manner of incorporeal yokai.	ABILITY:Medium Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Spirit Eater ~ Ectoplasmic Strikes|PRECLASS:1,Medium=3	ABILITY:Medium Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Spirit Eater ~ Consume Spirit|PRECLASS:1,Medium=7																																																																																																							COST:0	FACT:Medium_Archetype_HauntChanneler|True	FACT:Medium_Archetype_LocationChannel|True	FACT:Medium_Archetype_ConnectionChannel|True	FACT:Medium_CF_HauntChanneler|True	FACT:Medium_CF_LocationChannel|True	FACT:Medium_CF_ConnectionChannel|True																																														ASPECT:Archetype Base Class|Medium

