Mythmaker			KEY:Priest of the Fallen ~ Mythmaker		SOURCEPAGE:p.17	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Spiritualist Class Feature.SpecialQuality.Supernatural				DEFINE:MythmakerArchmage|0	DEFINE:MythmakerChampion|0	DEFINE:MythmakerGuardian|0	DEFINE:MythmakerHierophant|0	DEFINE:MythmakerMarshal|0	DEFINE:MythmakerTrickster|0	DESC:A priest of the fallen can channel many different hero-god phantoms, though only one at a time. These spirits will not suffer being confined in a mortal’s consciousness and must be manifested in ectoplasmic or incorporeal form or they return to the Ethereal Plane. They each have an emotional focus depending on their personality and retain some of their hero-god powers, determined by their mythic archetype. A priest of the fallen can channel a hero-god phantom with a ritual that takes 1 minute to perform. A priest of the fallen can channel only one hero-god phantom per 24 hours, but once channeled, a hero-god phantom remains until a new one is channeled.	DESC:&nl; This alters phantom and replaces shared consciousness.|!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Spiritualist Archetype ~ Priest of the Fallen	BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Mythmaker Hero-God|1
