Divine Vengeance				KEY:Medium ~ Psomeira ~ Divine Vengeance			SOURCEPAGE:p.15	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MediumClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural					SPELLS:Medium|CASTERLEVEL=MediumLVL|Align Weapon (Law Only)|PREVARGTEQ:CHASCORE,12	SPELLS:Medium|CASTERLEVEL=MediumLVL|Magic Weapon|Shield of Faith|PREVARGTEQ:CHASCORE,11	DESC:As a divine warrior, you can cast each of the following spells once per day: align weapon (lawful), magic weapon, and shield of faith. Use your medium level in place of a cleric level. These spells do not count toward your regular allotment of spells per day, but you must have a Charisma score of at least 10 + the spell’s level to cast them.
