#Ardril, the Would-Be King Spirit
Challenge					KEY:Medium ~ Ardril ~ Challenge				SOURCEPAGE:p.5	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MediumClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																		DESC:You gain the challenge ability as a cavalier of your level. When you challenge a foe, your attacks ignore any damage reduction your target has. In addition, you gain a +2 bonus on saving throws until the challenge ends.																																																																								ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Cavalier ~ Challenge																																																																																		BONUS:VAR|CavalierOrderChallengeBonus|(MediumLVL+3)/4	BONUS:VAR|CavalierChallengeLVL|MediumLVL	BONUS:VAR|CavalierChallengeTimes|(MediumLVL+2)/3	TEMPBONUS:PC|SAVE|ALL|2
Death Curse					KEY:Medium ~ Ardril ~ Death Curse				SOURCEPAGE:p.5	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MediumClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																		DESC:When you channel Ardril, you can select any two linnorm death curse rage powers. You can select different rage powers each time you channel Ardril. Treat your medium level as your barbarian level for the purpose of meeting prerequisites. You gain the benefit of these rage powers against challenged foes even if you are not raging. For each additional point of damage that would be dealt by a rage power, you deal 1d6 points of damage instead.																																																																																																																							BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Medium Death Curse|2
#Father of Legends
Song of Valor				KEY:Medium ~ Father of Legends ~ Song of Valor		SOURCEPAGE:p.5	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MediumClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																		DESC:As a standard action, you can begin a performance that fills allies with power and confidence. Any ally that participated in your seance who can hear your performance receives a +%1 morale bonus to Strength and Constitution. You can maintain this performance for %2 rounds. These rounds need not be consecutive. Maintaining your performance is a free action.|SpiritBonus|CHA+SpiritBonus
Saga of Future Kings			KEY:Medium ~ Father of Legends ~ Saga of Future Kings	SOURCEPAGE:p.5	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MediumClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																		DESC:Each ally who benefits from your song of valor gains DR/%1. In addition, when an ally affected by your song would be reduced to fewer than 0 hit points, she can attempt a Fortitude saving throw (DC = 10 + half the damage received). If the ally succeeds, she instead is reduced to 0 hit points.|SpiritBonus
